wirelay: wired's gentoo overlay - testing grounds and bleeding edge stuff

for all things to come :)

as of 2009/07/19 wirelay is in layman's overlay list
	layman -L
	layman -a wirelay

if you can't find it, you can always:
	layman -f -o http://github.com/wired/wirelay/raw/master/Documentation/wirelay.list -a wirelay
